            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nFor a better understanding of this text, we recommend reading: The first three chapters of the section **First steps**, in addition, the first chapter of the section **Understanding texts**",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team, First Steps",
                     "date" :  {"type" : "gregory", "year" : "2024", "month" : "-1", "day" : "-1" }
                  },
                  {
